<p id="mcetoc_1jatffl6km"> Documentación de Configuración Inicial</p>
<p>Este documento detalla los pasos de configuración inicial para la Raspberry Pi y el Mac mini.</p>
<div class="section-container">
<h2 id="mcetoc_1jatffl6kn" class="align-center"> Configuración Inicial de la Raspberry Pi (Sistema Operativo Raspberry Pi OS)</h2>
<div class="step">
<h3 id="mcetoc_1jatffl6ko">Paso 1: Bienvenida al Escritorio Pi</h3>
<div class="step-content"><figure class="post__image"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/WhatsApp-Image-2025-11-20-at-19.42.30.jpeg" alt="" width="265" height="589" sizes="(min-width: 920px) 703px, (min-width: 700px) calc(82vw - 35px), calc(100vw - 81px)" srcset="https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/responsive/WhatsApp-Image-2025-11-20-at-19.42.30-xs.jpeg 300w ,https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/responsive/WhatsApp-Image-2025-11-20-at-19.42.30-sm.jpeg 480w ,https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/responsive/WhatsApp-Image-2025-11-20-at-19.42.30-md.jpeg 768w ,https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/responsive/WhatsApp-Image-2025-11-20-at-19.42.30-lg.jpeg 1024w"></figure><br>
<p>Se muestra la pantalla de bienvenida al **Raspberry Pi Desktop**. Presiona **'Next'** para comenzar la configuración. Si se requiere, se solicita un reinicio para el auto-emparejamiento de dispositivos Bluetooth.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="step">
<h3 id="mcetoc_1jatffl6kp">Paso 2: Conexión a la Red WiFi</h3>
<div class="step-content"><figure class="post__image"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/WhatsApp-Image-2025-11-20-at-19.42.24.jpeg" alt="" width="220" height="489" sizes="(min-width: 920px) 703px, (min-width: 700px) calc(82vw - 35px), calc(100vw - 81px)" srcset="https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/responsive/WhatsApp-Image-2025-11-20-at-19.42.24-xs.jpeg 300w ,https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/responsive/WhatsApp-Image-2025-11-20-at-19.42.24-sm.jpeg 480w ,https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/responsive/WhatsApp-Image-2025-11-20-at-19.42.24-md.jpeg 768w ,https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/responsive/WhatsApp-Image-2025-11-20-at-19.42.24-lg.jpeg 1024w"></figure><br>
<p>Selecciona la red **'WiFi_AULA_ATECA'** de la lista y haz clic en **'Next'**.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="step">
<h3 id="mcetoc_1jatffl6kq">Paso 3: Contraseña de WiFi</h3>
<div class="step-content"><figure class="post__image"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/WhatsApp-Image-2025-11-20-at-19.42.23-1.jpeg" alt="" width="273" height="606" sizes="(min-width: 920px) 703px, (min-width: 700px) calc(82vw - 35px), calc(100vw - 81px)" srcset="https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/responsive/WhatsApp-Image-2025-11-20-at-19.42.23-1-xs.jpeg 300w ,https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/responsive/WhatsApp-Image-2025-11-20-at-19.42.23-1-sm.jpeg 480w ,https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/responsive/WhatsApp-Image-2025-11-20-at-19.42.23-1-md.jpeg 768w ,https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/responsive/WhatsApp-Image-2025-11-20-at-19.42.23-1-lg.jpeg 1024w"></figure><br>
<p>Introduce la contraseña de la red **'WiFi_AULA_ATECA'** y pulsa **'Next'** para conectar.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="step">
<h3 id="mcetoc_1jatffl6kr">Paso 4: Actualización de Software (Verificación)</h3>
<div class="step-content"><figure class="post__image"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/WhatsApp-Image-2025-11-20-at-19.42.22-1-2.jpeg" alt="" width="304" height="675" sizes="(min-width: 920px) 703px, (min-width: 700px) calc(82vw - 35px), calc(100vw - 81px)" srcset="https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/responsive/WhatsApp-Image-2025-11-20-at-19.42.22-1-2-xs.jpeg 300w ,https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/responsive/WhatsApp-Image-2025-11-20-at-19.42.22-1-2-sm.jpeg 480w ,https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/responsive/WhatsApp-Image-2025-11-20-at-19.42.22-1-2-md.jpeg 768w ,https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/responsive/WhatsApp-Image-2025-11-20-at-19.42.22-1-2-lg.jpeg 1024w"></figure><br>
<p>Se ofrece la opción de verificar y actualizar el sistema operativo y las aplicaciones. Pulsa **'Next'** para comenzar la comprobación y posible descarga/actualización, o **'Skip'** para continuar sin ella. Se descaraga TODO, esto puede tardar varios minutos, hay que tener paciencia</p>
<h3 id="mcetoc_1jatffl6ks">Paso 5: Crear USUARIO</h3>
<figure class="post__image"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/WhatsApp-Image-2025-11-20-at-19.42.24-1.jpeg" alt="" width="288" height="640" sizes="(min-width: 920px) 703px, (min-width: 700px) calc(82vw - 35px), calc(100vw - 81px)" srcset="https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/responsive/WhatsApp-Image-2025-11-20-at-19.42.24-1-xs.jpeg 300w ,https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/responsive/WhatsApp-Image-2025-11-20-at-19.42.24-1-sm.jpeg 480w ,https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/responsive/WhatsApp-Image-2025-11-20-at-19.42.24-1-md.jpeg 768w ,https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/responsive/WhatsApp-Image-2025-11-20-at-19.42.24-1-lg.jpeg 1024w"></figure>
<div class="step-content"><br>
<p>Creamos usuario y contraseña que vayamos a usar para la raspi.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="step">
<h3 id="mcetoc_1jatffl6kt">Paso 6: Elegir Navegador por Defecto</h3>
<div class="step-content"><figure class="post__image"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/Gemini_Generated_Image_l6l4qfl6l4qfl6l4.png" alt="" width="321" height="734" sizes="(min-width: 920px) 703px, (min-width: 700px) calc(82vw - 35px), calc(100vw - 81px)" srcset="https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/responsive/Gemini_Generated_Image_l6l4qfl6l4qfl6l4-xs.png 300w ,https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/responsive/Gemini_Generated_Image_l6l4qfl6l4qfl6l4-sm.png 480w ,https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/responsive/Gemini_Generated_Image_l6l4qfl6l4qfl6l4-md.png 768w ,https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/responsive/Gemini_Generated_Image_l6l4qfl6l4qfl6l4-lg.png 1024w"></figure><br>
<p>Selecciona el navegador web por defecto que deseas usar. En este caso se elige **Firefox**. También puedes marcar la opción para desinstalar el navegador no utilizado (Chromium).</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="section-container">
<h2 id="mcetoc_1jatffl6ku" class="align-center"> Configuración Inicial del Mac Mini (macOS)</h2>
<div class="step">
<h3 id="mcetoc_1jatffl6kv">Paso 1: Creación de Cuenta de Usuario</h3>
<div class="step-content"><figure class="post__image"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/WhatsApp-Image-2025-11-20-at-19.42.45-2.jpeg" alt="" width="461" height="335" sizes="(min-width: 920px) 703px, (min-width: 700px) calc(82vw - 35px), calc(100vw - 81px)" srcset="https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/responsive/WhatsApp-Image-2025-11-20-at-19.42.45-2-xs.jpeg 300w ,https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/responsive/WhatsApp-Image-2025-11-20-at-19.42.45-2-sm.jpeg 480w ,https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/responsive/WhatsApp-Image-2025-11-20-at-19.42.45-2-md.jpeg 768w ,https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/responsive/WhatsApp-Image-2025-11-20-at-19.42.45-2-lg.jpeg 1024w"></figure><br>
<p>Se procede a la creación de una cuenta de usuario local. Se debe introducir el nombre completo, nombre de cuenta y la contraseña.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="step">
<div class="step-content">
<p> </p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="step">
<h3 id="mcetoc_1jatffl6k10">Paso 2: Escritorio Final (Mac Mini)</h3>
<div class="step-content"><figure class="post__image"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/WhatsApp-Image-2025-11-20-at-19.42.44-2.jpeg" alt="" width="461" height="362" sizes="(min-width: 920px) 703px, (min-width: 700px) calc(82vw - 35px), calc(100vw - 81px)" srcset="https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/responsive/WhatsApp-Image-2025-11-20-at-19.42.44-2-xs.jpeg 300w ,https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/responsive/WhatsApp-Image-2025-11-20-at-19.42.44-2-sm.jpeg 480w ,https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/responsive/WhatsApp-Image-2025-11-20-at-19.42.44-2-md.jpeg 768w ,https://sergio-ops10.github.io/2damasi/media/posts/2/responsive/WhatsApp-Image-2025-11-20-at-19.42.44-2-lg.jpeg 1024w"></figure><br>
<p>Una vez completada la configuración y el inicio de sesión, se muestra el escritorio de macOS, listo para su uso.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<footer>
<p>Documentación generada el 25 de noviembre de 2025.</p>
